chain_zero_ref
--------------
l1: $ top $ by keep [top_i []]

chain_hyp_ref
-------------
l1: $ a $ by keep [keep [#1]]

chain_prev_line
---------------
l1: $ top $ by top_i []
l2: $ top $ by keep [keep [l1]]

chain_explicit_binding
----------------------
l1: $ top $ by keep [keep (a := $ top $) [top_i []]]

chain_two_level
---------------
l1: $ wrap top $ by wrap_i [keep [keep [top_i []]]]
